
Anyone who wants to mod this game, please do, it's boring right now. I will eventually try to add a way to save your world, but I tried and failed. 

Controls. 

Arrow keys:move
Z:place
X:remove
C:Change direction(You point in the direction you move)
Space: change block(On an un-moded game, this douse nill)


Moding:

Change the types var to add types.

HAVE FUN!   
